#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/extract_slice.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/extract_slice.md:4
msgid ""
"简介：从输入张量中按照操作指定的偏移量、大小和步幅参数提取一个张量。\n"
"原型：\n"
msgstr ""
"Introduction: Extract a tensor from the input tensor according to the offset, size, and stride parameters specified by the operation.  \n"
"Prototype:\n"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/extract_slice.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.extract_slice(\n"
"    ful,\n"
"    offsets,\n"
"    sizes,\n"
"    strides,\n"
"    _builder=None,\n"
"    _generator=None\n"
") -> tensor\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/extract_slice.md:8
msgid "## 2. OP 规格"
msgstr "## 2. OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/extract_slice.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/extract_slice.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数名           | 类型                | 说明                                                             |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `ful`        | `tensor`          | 要提取切片的源张量                                                     |\n"
"| `offsets`       | `tuple of ints`    | 切片在各个维度上的起始偏移量                                                        |\n"
"| `sizes`     | `tuple of ints`    | 切片在各个维度上的大小 |\n"
"| `strides` | `tuple of ints` | 切片在各个维度上的步长                                             |\n"
"| `_builder` |- | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用                                            |\n"
"| `_generator`   | -               | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用                                                |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type             | Description                                                    |\n"
"| ------------- | ---------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `ful`         | `tensor`         | The source tensor from which to extract the slice              |\n"
"| `offsets`     | `tuple of ints`  | Starting offsets of the slice along each dimension             |\n"
"| `sizes`       | `tuple of ints`  | Sizes of the slice along each dimension                        |\n"
"| `strides`     | `tuple of ints`  | Strides of the slice along each dimension                      |\n"
"| `_builder`    | -                | Reserved parameter, external calls not supported currently     |\n"
"| `_generator`  | -                | Reserved parameter, external calls not supported currently     |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/extract_slice.md:14
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"`tensor`：提取的切片张量\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"`tensor`: the extracted slice tensor\n"

